Module.Content:
<html>

<head>
        <style type="text/css">

body {
    background-color: rgb(37,37,37)
}

button {
  align-items: center;
  background-image: linear-gradient(144deg,#AF40FF, #5B42F3 50%,#00DDEB);
  border: 0;
  border-radius: 8px;
  box-shadow: rgba(151, 65, 252, 0.2) 0 15px 30px -5px;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  color: #FFFFFF;
  display: flex;
  font-family: Phantomsans, sans-serif;
  font-size: 20px;
  justify-content: center;
  line-height: 1em;
  width: 100%;
  padding: 3px;
  text-decoration: none;
  user-select: none;
  -webkit-user-select: none;
  touch-action: manipulation;
  white-space: nowrap;
  cursor: pointer;
  margin: 0;
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  ms-transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
}

button:active,
button-64:hover {
  outline: 0;
}

button span {
  background-color: rgb(5, 6, 45);
  padding: 16px 24px;
  border-radius: 6px;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  transition: 300ms;
}

button:hover span {
  background: none;
}

@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .button-64 {
    font-size: 24px;
    min-width: 196px;
  }
}

        </style>
</head>



<script>

function full() {
let html = atob("")
document.getElementById("container").innerHTML = html
}

</script>
<div id="container" width="100%" height="100%">
    <button onclick="full();">Open External Launcher</button>
</div>
</html>
